ClusterSignificanceExtras
  • Reference

Specificity test results dataset.

Output from the specificityTest function with default arguments.

specificityTestResults

Format

data.frame

points

The number of points per group.

rep

The repitition.

pValuePcp

The pValue from ClusterSignificance with 10^4 iterations.

Value

data.frame

Examples
